  }, "The third season of Anime"), ", which I just finished watching, was also excellent. I loved the description of the last scene in the final episode and realized the significance of that one scene, which is a big part of the narrative itself, which I didn't realize when watching the manga.\nI try not to spoil anything when I write on my blog (by marking it in the title or subtitle). But what I don't want to say is that I really want you to watch the final scene of the third period anime."), mdx("p", null, "I know no one will see this, but I hope you'll watch it and feel similar to me."), mdx("p", null, "(End)"));
